			<h1 class="article-title"><a href="index.html?p=7961">《以色列一个民族的重生》</a></h1>
			<div class="article-meta">
				<span class="item">2020-12-02</span>
												<span class="item">分类：<a href="biography/index.html" rel="category tag">传记</a></span>
